				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-V%C5%A9-X%E1%BB%A9ng/C%E1%BA%A3m-l%C6%B0u-vong/poem-2eUGsCyGotGtviV5C0QIDw">Cảm lưu vong - 感流亡</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-V%C5%A9-X%E1%BB%A9ng/author-gsSbrX8mxDOHV8mbduxYMg">Vương Vũ Xứng</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-T%E1%BB%AD-Ngang/C%E1%BA%A3m-ng%E1%BB%99-k%E1%BB%B3-25/poem-c6g39E3xPTFyf_DWOB-GYw">Cảm ngộ kỳ 25 - 感遇其二十五</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-T%E1%BB%AD-Ngang/author-KAeplXpuQBYC4UQBLqb_RQ">Trần Tử Ngang</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Chu-ph%E1%BB%A5ng-h%C3%A0nh/poem-ncflj_afqryTFi6W6-MWNA">Chu phụng hành - 朱鳳行</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-%C4%90%C3%ACnh-H%E1%BB%95/C%E1%BB%B1u-ca-c%C6%A1/poem-O9N-VHhlreCYXrMdS3CXdg">Cựu ca cơ - 舊歌姬</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-%C4%90%C3%ACnh-H%E1%BB%95/author-qsdCXtvu8PM8SdkWmraV5A">Phạm Đình Hổ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%C3%A2n-Nh%C3%A2n-Trung/%C4%90%E1%BA%A1i-B%E1%BA%A3o-tam-ni%C3%AAn-Nh%C3%A2m-Tu%E1%BA%A5t-khoa-ti%E1%BA%BFn-s%C4%A9-%C4%91%E1%BB%81-danh-k%C3%BD/poem-lmPI_Y7GazogxyWzI82qMg">Đại Bảo tam niên Nhâm Tuất khoa tiến sĩ đề danh ký - 大寶弎年壬戌科進士題名記</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%C3%A2n-Nh%C3%A2n-Trung/author-eOFIe3QgfrDzlduYauxtuQ">Thân Nhân Trung</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-B%C3%A1-Qu%C3%A1t/%C4%90%E1%BB%99c-d%E1%BA%A1-Nh%E1%BA%ADt-nh%E1%BA%ADt-duy-s%E1%BA%A7u-th%E1%BB%AD/poem-PCsttpPNSVftis9tQ4kKug">Độc dạ (Nhật nhật duy sầu thử) - 獨夜（日日惟愁暑）</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-B%C3%A1-Qu%C3%A1t/author-2eyz08Vw3mwjAHFJik43sA">Cao Bá Quát</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%C3%A0-C%E1%BA%A3nh-Minh/Kh%E1%BB%91c-%E1%BA%A5u-n%E1%BB%AF-h%C3%A0nh/poem-f_Ib9mZaokq393Mz7dBe6g">Khốc ấu nữ hành - 哭幼女行</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%C3%A0-C%E1%BA%A3nh-Minh/author-wg6EAaIQ8OL-TAAIuNs-Kg">Hà Cảnh Minh</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/K%E1%BB%B3-%C4%90%E1%BB%93ng/Khuy%E1%BA%BFn-h%E1%BB%8Dc/poem-HPqEmUiX0JHD3yZpQ6V6ZQ">Khuyến học - 勸學</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/K%E1%BB%B3-%C4%90%E1%BB%93ng/author-03ZNaWfxP9_K2e7vJXYXyw">Kỳ Đồng</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/L%E1%BA%ADp-thu-h%E1%BA%ADu-%C4%91%E1%BB%81/poem-Z9yS8e8fQYCIh3f-sCfiXw">Lập thu hậu đề - 立秋後題</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tu%E1%BB%87-T%C4%A9nh-thi%E1%BB%81n-s%C6%B0/M%E1%BB%99c-mi%C3%AAn/poem-Y3KOp2ZfxW261U6BFlCvUg">Mộc miên - 木棉</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tu%E1%BB%87-T%C4%A9nh-thi%E1%BB%81n-s%C6%B0/author-9Mr6hsa5RsMoTXWLKUTJEg">Tuệ Tĩnh thiền sư</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
